WEBVTT

26:05.960 --> 26:07.680 line:80%
He had the guts to smash my shop,

26:07.680 --> 26:09.610 line:80%
but now he's hiding like a coward?

26:10.040 --> 26:11.240 line:80%
What's going on here?

26:11.680 --> 26:12.590 line:80%
Gentlemen,

26:12.720 --> 26:13.350 line:80%
let's wait for our shopkeeper

26:13.350 --> 26:15.000 line:80%
before we discuss anything.

26:15.040 --> 26:17.310 line:80%
What's all the noise?
